The '''Xenvaer Civic Auditorium''' was located in [[Xenvaer]] on [[Alsakan/Legends|Alsakan]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], it hosted a large [[Refugee Relief Movement/Legends|Refugee Relief Movement]] [[Refugee Relief Movement fundraiser|fundraiser]] attended by [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and members of his [[Loyalist Committee/Legends|Loyalist Committee]]. The fundraiser was estimated to have raised 75 million [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] for the Refugee Relief Movement.<ref name="HNNfundraiser" />

